April 23 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Wednesday. To inform us of other job changes, email to moves@thomsonreuters.com.

CANTOR FITZGERALD WEALTH PARTNERS Cantor Fitzgerald Wealth Partners, launched in November 2013 by institutional trading firm Cantor Fitzgerald LP [CNTOR.UL], has hired Lowell "Bob" Serhus as chief investment officer to guide the firm's financial advisers on portfolio and risk management, with a focus on alternative investments. [ID:nL2N0NE1KE]  BANK OF AMERICA CORP <BAC.N> Lisa Carnoy has joined U.S. Trust, the private banking unit of Bank of America, as division executive for its Northeast and metropolitan New York region. [ID:nL2N0NE1UA]  AMP CAPITAL